Exercice 1

Question 1

data("roomwidth",package="HSAUR")

Question 2

convert <- ifelse(roomwidth$unit=="feet",1,3.28)
feet <- roomwidth$unit=="feet"
metre <- !feet
y <- roomwidth$width*convert

Question 3

Tobs <- mean(y[feet])-mean(y[metre])
Tobs
## [1] -8.858893

Question 4

meandiffs <- double(9999)
for (i in 1:length(meandiffs)){
  sy <- sample(y)
  meandiffs[i] <- mean(sy[feet])-mean(sy[metre])
}
layout(1)
hist(meandiffs)
abline(v=Tobs,lty=2,col="red")
abline(v=-Tobs,lty=2,col="red")

Graphique annoté de la distribution permutationnelle
Download Perm_Rplot_wCOMMENTS.pdf

Question 5

greater <- abs(meandiffs) > abs(Tobs)
mean(greater)
## [1] 0.00770077

Question 6

binom.test(sum(greater),length(greater))$conf.int
## [1] 0.006081968 0.009615372
## attr(,"conf.level")
## [1] 0.95

Étude des différences des médianes

Mobs <- median(y[feet])-median(y[metre])
Mobs
## [1] -7.2
mediandiffs <- double(9999)
for (i in 1:length(mediandiffs)){
  sy <- sample(y)
  mediandiffs[i] <- median(sy[feet])-median(sy[metre])
}
layout(1)
hist(mediandiffs)
abline(v=Mobs,lty=2,col="red")
abline(v=-Mobs,lty=2,col="red")

Question 5 pour les médianes

greaterM <- abs(mediandiffs) > abs(Mobs)
mean(greaterM)
## [1] 0.00150015

Question 6 pour les médianes

binom.test(sum(greaterM),length(greaterM))$conf.int
## [1] 0.000839858 0.002473064
## attr(,"conf.level")
## [1] 0.95
